<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px] text-secondary" data-icon="lock" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">lock</span>
<span class="text-[10px] font-label text-outline tracking-wider uppercase">End-to-End Encrypted</span>
